data.name: SQL_GW_Hertz_2024_V2
data.queryText:
SELECT 
TI.passengerseqid,TI.uniid, TI.emailaddress, TI.pnrlocatorid, TI.servicestartcity_desc, TI.lenguaje, 
TI.serviceendcityfinal_desc, TI.region, TI.categoria, gender, namefirst, namelast,  
pnrcreatedate, marketingflightnbr, equipo, 
goldenw, pais_compra, classofservice, servicestartdatetime,serviceenddatetimefinal, servicestartcity, serviceendcityfinal,
TI.go_back AS GoOrBack, vcrcreatedate, birth_date, rfmcategory, customercategory, npscategory, celular, 
frequenttravelernbr, tier, topamx, topstd, marketingairlinecode, operatingairlinecode, 
operatingflightnbr, basefareamt, basefarecurrcode, cabina, horas, servicestartcity_od, servicestartcity_od_desc,
serviceendcityfinal_od, serviceendcityfinal_od_desc, tramo, ow_rt, canal, region_od, fecha_actual,
upgrade_ind, premium_seat_ind, seguro_ind, concierge_ind, disc_pass_ind, kit_experto, primaleta_ind,
cbx_ind, vla_vrd, primarydocnbr,serviceendcityfinal_od_des_en, serviceendcityfinal_od_des_es,
servicestartcity_od_des_en, servicestartcity_desc_en, servicestartcity_od_des_es, serviceendcityfinal_des_es, serviceendcityfinal_des_en,
servicestartcity_desc_es
FROM
{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/c9b72e43-b39b-ef11-a5cb-5cba2c759758/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/c9b72e43-b39b-ef11-a5cb-5cba2c759758/data/name}}] AS TI 
WHERE TI.pais_compra NOT IN ('NL')
AND TI.serviceendcityfinal_desc NOT IN ('MEDELLIN','BOGOTA','TOCUMEN-PANAMA')
AND TI.servicestartcity_desc NOT IN ('MEDELLIN','BOGOTA','TOCUMEN-PANAMA')

data.name: SQL_HERTZ_COMPLETE_2024_V2
data.queryText:
select uniid,emailaddress, servicestartdatetime,

(SELECT keyword_place 
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/bd71bd25-49ea-eb11-b828-48df37d1de8a/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/bd71bd25-49ea-eb11-b828-48df37d1de8a/data/name}}] WHERE LTRIM(RTRIM(Codigo))=UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(serviceendcityfinal)))) AS [keyword-place],

(SELECT City 
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/c903ce91-9fcd-e911-a2e8-1402ec9366a1/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/c903ce91-9fcd-e911-a2e8-1402ec9366a1/data/name}}] WHERE UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(IATACode)))=UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(servicestartcity)))) AS servicestartcity_desc,


(SELECT City 
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/c903ce91-9fcd-e911-a2e8-1402ec9366a1/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/c903ce91-9fcd-e911-a2e8-1402ec9366a1/data/name}}] WHERE UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(IATACode)))=UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(serviceendcityfinal)))) AS serviceendcityfinal_desc,


(SELECT HertzLocatorID 
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/c903ce91-9fcd-e911-a2e8-1402ec9366a1/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/c903ce91-9fcd-e911-a2e8-1402ec9366a1/data/name}}] WHERE UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(IATACode)))=UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(serviceendcityfinal)))) AS LocatorID,


(SELECT Identificador 
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/bd71bd25-49ea-eb11-b828-48df37d1de8a/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/bd71bd25-49ea-eb11-b828-48df37d1de8a/data/name}}] WHERE LTRIM(RTRIM(Codigo))=UPPER(LTRIM(RTRIM(serviceendcityfinal)))) AS identificador,

DATEADD (dd , 2 , servicestartdatetime ) as DropEndDate
, ISNULL (serviceenddatetimefinal , ServiceStartDateTime ) as ServiceEndDateTimeFinal,

CONVERT(varchar,DropEndDate,23) as [FechaSalida],

CONVERT(varchar,ServiceEndDateTimeFinal,23) as [FechaEntrada],

servicestartcity_od, serviceendcityfinal_od,pnrlocatorid,lenguaje,region,categoria, gender, namefirst, namelast,  pnrcreatedate, marketingflightnbr, equipo, 
goldenw, pais_compra, classofservice, servicestartcity, serviceendcityfinal, go_back AS GoOrBack,passengerseqid

From {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2e7dcf07-009e-ef11-a5cb-5cba2c759758/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/2e7dcf07-009e-ef11-a5cb-5cba2c759758/data/name}}]
